data.description: Super Spacious & Beautiful 4 Level Split on Private Country Lot! Follow the stamped concrete walkway to the covered front porch with trex deck to the front door! Living Room entry features a front bay window & engineered wood flooring. Granite & Stainless Kitchen with slider exit to rear deck & side exit to laundry room & pantry.  From the laundry, enter the 2 car side load garage with automatic openers.  The upper level features a Primary Bedroom with slider to private deck area and full bath, 2 additional bedrooms and a 2nd full bath off the hall. The first lower level is a great room with sectioned areas for flexible living space, featuring a masonry wood-burning fireplace, engineered wood flooring, a slider exit to a lovely flagstone-style patio, and a full bath with a jetted tub. The 4th level gives more recreation space, a separate den and the utility & storage room. The multi-section deck at the rear which adjoins an extra large patio, a cozy side patio, the covered front porch - all offer incredible outdoor living. Try some home gardening and utilize the greenhouse! 1 Year Buyer Preferred Cinch Warranty is included. This property offers lovely decor & updates throughout as well as convenience to schools, shopping and commuter routes, yet it's a private, peaceful setting "away from it all"!
